rows.label: qst650208_msg0001
rows.name: Mehmeh! You return!

rows.label: qst650208_msg0002
rows.name:
Expression on faces tell Senzo
that test drive was success?

rows.label: qst650208_msg0003
rows.name:
Naturally it was.
You can't possibly have expected me
to fail, can you?

rows.label: qst650208_msg0004
rows.name:
With support from Hanabuster, Hana
could give 110% energy output.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0005
rows.name:
That great to hear!
Was anything needing tune-up?

rows.label: qst650208_msg0006
rows.name:
Hana and Hana Mk. II both operating
with no glitches whatsoever.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0007
rows.name: My performance was also flawless.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0008
rows.name: Great news, great news.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0009
rows.name:
In that case, Senzo give Hanabuster
to friends, as planned.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0010
rows.name:
I'm think I'm going to enjoy your
company, friends and companions
of Hana-san.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0011
rows.name: Likewise!

rows.label: qst650208_msg0012
rows.name: Meh-ho-ho!

rows.label: qst650208_msg0013
rows.name:
Then it about time for Senzo to go
back into hiding.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0014
rows.name: Grampypon not want to see Dadapon?

rows.label: qst650208_msg0015
rows.name:
Tatezo now living perfectly content
life without his dadapon. Maybe best
to leave that way.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0016
rows.name:
After all, great achievement of make
Hana and Kiku also possible because
Senzo not in picture anymore.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0017
rows.name:
I believe it better for Tora and Tatezo
to stand on own feet, keep inventing
wondrous inventions!

rows.label: qst650208_msg0018
rows.name: Tora have complicated feelings now...

rows.label: qst650208_msg0019
rows.name: ...Grampypon, will we meet again?

rows.label: qst650208_msg0020
rows.name: But of course!

rows.label: qst650208_msg0021
rows.name: Dear friends of Tora...

rows.label: qst650208_msg0022
rows.name:
Please take good care of Tora
and Hana, and Hana Mk. II, and
Hanabuster too.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0023
rows.name: You've got it!

rows.label: qst650208_msg0024
rows.name: We're a caring bunch, really!

rows.label: qst650208_msg0025
rows.name: Please take care of self, Professor.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0026
rows.name:
Thank you. Senzo surely will.
Until we meet again!

rows.label: qst650208_msg0101
rows.name: Say, now that I think about it...

rows.label: qst650208_msg0102
rows.name:
What's that name mean, "Hanabuster"?
I totally forgot to ask...

rows.label: qst650208_msg0103
rows.name: Yes, it has been bothering me too.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0104
rows.name: Hanabuster, do you know?

rows.label: qst650208_msg0105
rows.name:
Of course I know.
Hana-san chose it for me.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0106
rows.name: Hana choose name like that?

rows.label: qst650208_msg0107
rows.name: Indeed.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0108
rows.name:
Hana choose most proper-sounding
name from list of three provided by
Professor Senzo.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0109
rows.name: What do you mean, proper-sounding...?

rows.label: qst650208_msg0110
rows.name: Three top ideas of Professor were...

rows.label: qst650208_msg0111
rows.name:
Number 1:
Hana Obey Powered Panzer Inferno.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0112
rows.name:
Number 2:
Senzo presents: New Hana XL
Deluxe.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0113
rows.name: And number 3 was Hanabuster.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0114
rows.name: That's one hell of a choice...

rows.label: qst650208_msg0115
rows.name:
Yes, naming sense of Grampypon
always was notoriously bad...

rows.label: qst650208_msg0116
rows.name:
I can definitely see why you'd choose
"Hanabuster" over the other two...

rows.label: qst650208_msg0117
rows.name:
As added bit of trivia, name meant to
suggest "enough power to take down
even Hana".

rows.label: qst650208_msg0118
rows.name:
Hana think that slightly in bad taste,
but then again, what do Hana know.
Coolness of name is paramount.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0119
rows.name:
Hana got that right! Make choice
is correct. Tora very proud!

rows.label: qst650208_msg0120
rows.name:
To quote great Nopon scholar,
meh-ho-ho.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0121
rows.name:
Well, I feel a lot better knowing where
the name came from. Let's keep up
the good work, Hanabuster!

rows.label: qst650208_msg0122
rows.name: Yes, please do.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0123
rows.name:
I myself will undoubtedly excel enough
to make you swoon, Ma'am.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0124
rows.name:
I'm sure that together, we'll make
your masterpon prouder still.

rows.label: qst650208_msg0125
rows.name:
Hana not think ego of Masterpon
need any more stroking, to be fair...
